itionally, if you are in a Performer Order, as a Complete Common Project order action, the character may roll a Performance skill check to write a new play, script, or symphony. The resulting work may be commissioned by a patron, but can also be sold to a willing buyer at a price of 20 times the result of a Performance skill check in silver pieces, or can be used in your own performances, providing a +2 each time you perform it that year, due to the freshness of the work.</span><br></span></p>","save":"","skill":"Performance","magic":false,"effort":0,"time":"","range":""},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"tyoa","systemVersion":"0.1.0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1675984103641,"modifiedTime":1675984559742,"lastModifiedBy":"vtQVXu8um2tryua5"},"_id":"SumTaA8dNbB2fy5y","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"vtQVXu8um2tryua5":3}}
